{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"a1caaf9320","title":"忽然想到（杂文）","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"bf6eb1b63d","index":0,"year":1956,"month":8,"day":8,"articleId":"a1caaf9320"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3aae6e8366","name":"中共中央高级党校"},{"id":"de0adac7c8","name":"姚北桦"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a2644d29ed","type":"title","text":"忽然想到（杂文）","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"dc1e93cce9","type":"authors","text":"中共中央高级党校姚北桦","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"903ce170a5","type":"subtitle","text":"（姚北桦：新闻班第三班第一支部学员；入学前为江苏《新华日报》副刊主编）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"87866bbb6c","type":"paragraph","text":"[原编者按：这是姚北桦在1956年8月写的一篇污蔑新社会里“连读报也没有自由”的杂文。发表于新华日报1956年8月8日“副刊”。署名：司空见。全文如下。]","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"49fca1a4fe","type":"paragraph","text":"据说某学校有位教师因爱看上海某小报，也被人指为有“思想问题”。理由是：上海者，花花世界也，爱看花花世界的小报者，一定是羡慕花花世界的生活方式者也。结论是：资产阶级思想无疑。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"fbfd1d359f","type":"paragraph","text":"乍听的时候，觉得这种事情实在好笑；转而一想，又似乎觉得不值一笑；但是想而又想，却觉得严重起来了。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"b25b52a28a","type":"paragraph","text":"按照上述公式推论，岂不事事都可能成为“问题”？比如，北京是历代帝王的都城，如果爱看北京的报纸，就会有封建思想之嫌。准此，南京的报纸也不能看，因为南京曾是国民党反动派的首都……。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"37a679b09f","type":"paragraph","text":"想不到在看报这件日常小事上，也有这么大的“帽子”。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"},{"id":"c4c2ab6d9b","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：中共中央高级党校校部办公室印；共印1800份，发全校学员和有关干部。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320"}],"page":{"id":"78a4ebd4ac","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"a1caaf9320","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}